column3: “definitely a good strain but not a strong one. tastes slightly like gummy bears if you sip coffee before you smoke it 🍵🖒”
“I chilled out, but got really motivated to get stuff done. was good (not the best) for my pain, but a good combination for puff and work, as I didn't feel altered and was more productive.”
“Smooth & Fruity. Can't go wrong. With a immediate relaxer like this.”
“Very nice strain! I got high like a fuckin skyscraper. Really recommend this strain for anyone who wants to get really stoned.”
